  "title": "Mining Utility",
  "description": "Utility items & blocks for your mining pleasure!",
  "body": "**Mining Utility** is a small utility mod to ease your difficulties while mining. It offers the following:\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"https://imgur.com/C5DHDXb.png\" alt=\"escape_rope\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Escape Rope</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Escape ropes can be used 16 times to teleport to any location on the world set previously, but that<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> must be on the same dimension</span>.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Right-Click to teleport, Shift-Right-Click to set teleport.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"https://imgur.com/AYRXGjh.png\" alt=\"escape_rope\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mini Torch</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Crafted with a torch, mini-torchs are tiny, easy to craft and resourceful. Lights up the same as the regular torch.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"https://imgur.com/7XtXwut.png\" alt=\"escape_rope\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Mining Helmet</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><br /><em>Equipped at head, mining helmets give infinite night vision and slight protection against the dangers of the caves.<br /></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"https://imgur.com/b78yCXU.png\" alt=\"escape_rope\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Rope Ladder</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>One-Use ladder than expands downward until the configured block limit (default: 64).</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"https://imgur.com/QtSoy0b.png\" alt=\"escape_rope\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Rope Ladder (Inverted)</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><br /><em>One-Use ladder than expands upward until the configured block limit (default: 64).</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/G4PjhEf\"> <img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/707435077679841350/embed.png?style=banner2&amp;v=2\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"76\" /> </a></p>",
